  "_comment": "Open house-number overlay catalog \u2014 OpenAddresses address POINTS, per US state, built to PMTiles by scripts/build-address-region.sh (resolves the source's current OpenAddresses job) and hosted on the `address-overlays` GitHub release. The app STREAMS them and renders the `number` field as a house-number SymbolLayer where OSM lacks addr:housenumber. Only states with an OpenAddresses `statewide` address source are listed (42); county-only states use source='us/<st>/*' \u2192 build-address-region.sh aggregates every OpenAddresses source under that prefix. World countries are a follow-up. bbox=[S,W,N,E] (Geofabrik state bounds; PR hand-set). source = the OpenAddresses source path.",
